graph TD
    A[Post new payment amount, date & method] --> B[Insert Payment record: status = Pending]
    B --> C{Trigger fires after insert}
    C --> D[Log Completed Payment Alert]
    D --> E[Process payment via gateway simulation]
    E --> F{Is payment Completed or Failed?}
    F -- Completed --> G[Send success alert email]
    F -- Failed --> H[Send failure alert email]
    G --> I[Recalculate Application Total Payments rollup]
    I --> J[Reduce Application Outstanding Balance]
